channel.title: What song is this?
channel.description:
I have been hearing a song on the radio a lot lately and I likeee it. My Shazam is broken so idk what it is called. This is the only part I know
It's like
"What you want, what you want, dum dum dum dum de dum."
They literally say dum dum dum and stuff. It is stuck in my head but idk the name. Anyone know it? Google was no help.
